### --- CHAT ---

### Fetch Chats
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/fetch
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Access/Create Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "TARGET_USER_ID"
}

### Create Group Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/createGroup
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Team Group",
  "userIds": ["USER_ID_1", "USER_ID_2"]
}

### Add Member to Group
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat/addMember
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "CHAT_ID",
  "userIds": ["USER_ID_3"]
}

### Remove Member from Group
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat/removeMember
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "CHAT_ID",
  "userId": "USER_ID_3"
}


